- Return only the fields the caller is authorized to see.
- Don't hardcode user data in source; load from a data layer so it can't be accidentally committed with real PII.

## 5. Logging & observability

- Replace `console.log` with a structured logger (`pino` or `winston`) so log lines are parseable and timestamps/levels are consistent.
