- [ ] `helmet`, disable `x-powered-by`
- [ ] Body size limits
- [ ] Rate limiting
- [ ] Validate every `params`/`query`/`body` field with an allowlist schema
- [ ] `asyncHandler` + centralized error middleware that never leaks stack traces
- [ ] 404 handler
- [ ] Explicit CORS policy
- [ ] No PII in unauthenticated responses
- [ ] Structured logging with request IDs
- [ ] Config from env, validated at boot
- [ ] Graceful shutdown and process-level error handlers

