`unhandledRejection` and `uncaughtException` are not captured, so failures exit silently or crash without logging.

### 3. No security headers
Missing `helmet` (or equivalent) — no CSP, no `X-Content-Type-Options`, `Strict-Transport-Security`, `X-Frame-Options`, etc.

