| Rate limiting | `express-rate-limit` | Mitigates brute-force & DoS |
| Validation | `express-validator` (`isEmail`, `escape`, `trim`, length caps) | Prevents injection, malformed input |
| Error handling | Centralized handler, no stack leakage in prod | Avoids info disclosure |
| PII | Remove `email` from list response | Minimizes data exposure |
| Process hygiene | `SIGTERM`/`unhandledRejection`/`uncaughtException` handlers | Clean shutdown, visibility into crashes |
| Config | `process.env.PORT` | Avoids hardcoded assumptions |

