| **High** | Add centralized error handler; remove `x-powered-by`; add `helmet` |
| **High** | Split `app.listen` out of `app.js` so tests don't bind a port |
| **High** | Validate/parse `process.env.PORT` |
| **Medium** | Add rate limiting and body-size limits |
| **Medium** | Gate PII (emails) behind auth |
| **Medium** | Graceful shutdown on SIGTERM/SIGINT |
| **Low** | Request logging, 404 handler, `unhandledRejection` trap |

