| **Rate limiting** | Apply `express-rate-limit` per-IP at minimum; per-user for authenticated routes. |
| **CORS** | Don't enable `cors()` with defaults (`*`) — specify an allowlist of origins. |
| **Logging PII** | The `/users` endpoint logs emails; ensure logs redact email, tokens, cookies. |
| **Secrets** | Never hardcode; validate required env vars at startup and fail loudly if missing. |
| **Dependencies** | Run `npm audit` in CI; pin versions; use `npm ci` in production. |

